- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is another likely category as the paper presents a structured migration process for multi-component enterprise applications, which is related to software engineering. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper presents a multi-criteria-based selection algorithm, which is related to algorithms. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper presents an implementation of the CloudGenius framework, which may involve programming languages.
